@HostAddress = http://localhost:5000

### 开发测试 Token
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/v1/auth/dev-token

### ── 卡片接口 ──

### 创建卡片
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/v1/cards
Authorization: Bearer <Token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "测试知识卡片",
  "sourceText": "原文摘录",
  "summary": "简短摘要",
  "sourceUrl": "https://example.com",
  "tags": ["AI", "工具"]
}

### 卡片列表
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/v1/cards?status=all&sort=updatedAt&order=desc
Authorization: Bearer <Token>

### 卡片列表（搜索）
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/v1/cards?keyword=AI&tag=工具
Authorization: Bearer <Token>

### 卡片详情
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/v1/cards/{id}
Authorization: Bearer <Token>

### 更新卡片
PATCH {{HostAddress}}/api/v1/cards/{id}
Authorization: Bearer <Token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "summary": "更新后的摘要",
  "status": "done"
}

### 归档卡片
PATCH {{HostAddress}}/api/v1/cards/{id}/archive
Authorization: Bearer <Token>

### 软删除卡片
DELETE {{HostAddress}}/api/v1/cards/{id}
Authorization: Bearer <Token>

### ── 回收站 ──

### 回收站列表
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/v1/cards/deleted
Authorization: Bearer <Token>

### 恢复卡片
PATCH {{HostAddress}}/api/v1/cards/{id}/restore
Authorization: Bearer <Token>

### 彻底删除
DELETE {{HostAddress}}/api/v1/cards/{id}/permanent
Authorization: Bearer <Token>

### ── 标签与工作台 ──

### 标签汇总
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/v1/cards/tags
Authorization: Bearer <Token>

### 工作台概览
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/v1/cards/overview
Authorization: Bearer <Token>

### ── 用户 ──

### 用户信息
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/v1/user/profile
Authorization: Bearer <Token>
